data.description: Welcome to this wonderful 5 bed + office, 3 bath home in the heart of Windsor! Updates throughout the home include solid wood floors, kitchen cabinets, doors, newer windows, roof, siding, paint and more. Basement features a flex area that could be used as a 2nd kitchen, storage, work shop, or additional laundry. The oversized 2 car garage loads from the alley and offers off-street parking with NO HOA. This home has been well cared for and has newer furnace, a/c, water heater, and all major kitchen appliances included. ADA compliant features throughout. Within walking distance to the lake, old town shops, restaurants, parks, and schools. Qualified VA buyers could potentially assume $315k loan at a 2.375% interest rate.
